{"tid":2115167,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普制裁發威 日企紛排除中國設備","createTime":"2020-07-19T10:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T10:25:39.000Z","uid":75656,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6dd4546d97d0c06144144c43afdd89bde084fc2","tid":2115167,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"美國政府將在8月13日起，限制華為、海康威視、大華、海能達、中興通訊等5中企的聯邦採購案；據《日經新聞》報導，此舉可能將影響800多間日企，包含軟銀、日本電信電話（NTT）等企業均表示，會逐漸將屬於中企的設備排除，因此該報導稱，此舉最終可能將加速美中經濟脫鉤。<br />\n<br />\n2019財年美國聯邦採購額高達5800億美元（約新台幣17.3兆元），其中對日企的採購額為15億美元，而從8月13日起，必須要取得未使用遭制裁中企的產品，才能參與聯邦採購競標。<br />\n<br />\n採用部分遭制裁中企產品的NTT對外表示，為了確保子公司NTT Data與美國政府的合約，將在生效日之前將這些中企產品排除掉，而且「之後也不會使用」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3232581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3232581&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pvZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=b1fd0095\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3232581&h=5147e539\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3232581</a>"},{"pid":"7d7787e4ae279f479c4cb0136b4d6c09a1a799d4","tid":2115167,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c5348d513232bd4cbfd47a94e983466176f70e","tid":2115167,"uid":170819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6d57e7c0d73551dfd05468ab67530b8364fc065","tid":2115167,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\"